                  <paragraph>The approximate buffer capacity of Elliotts B
Solution is 1.1 X 10<sup>-2</sup> equivalents when the challenge solution is
0.01 N HCl and 7.8 X 10<sup>-3</sup> equivalents when the challenge solution is
0.01 N NaOH.<content styleCode="sup">
                        <linkHtml href="#references">1</linkHtml>
                     </content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <br/>Compatibility studies with methotrexate sodium
and cytarabine indicate these drugs are physically compati­ble with Elliotts B
Solution.<paragraph>
                     <br/>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20101210"/>
