                           </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                           <td>67871-007-10<br/>
                           </td>
                           <td>10 mL ampule<br/>
                           </td>
                        </tr>
                     </tbody>
                  </table>Elliotts B Solution is available in single-use clear glass ampules, packaged 10 ampules per box.<br/>
                  <br/>Store at controlled room temperature, 20º-25ºC (68º-77ºF) [See USP].<br/>
                  <br/>
                  <content styleCode="bold">Preservative Free. </content> Discard unused portion.  Use only if solution is clear and ampule is intact.<br/>
